OL,3,CCouncil looking for two lorries after
OL,4,C30 tonnes of rubbish dumped
OL,6,FWatch as diggers move in to begin
OL,7,Fclearing the rubbish
OL,9,FCouncil investigators are appealing
OL,10,Ffor more footage after two tipper-type
OL,11,Florries were caught on CCTV when they
OL,12,Fbelieve 30 tonnes of rubbish was
OL,13,Fdumped on a Lichfield road.
OL,15,FLichfield District Council believes
OL,16,Fthe building waste, including
OL,17,Fhousehold rubbish, was fly-tipped in
OL,18,FWatery Lane, near Curborough, at 11 pm
OL,19,Fon Sunday and 12.45 am on Monday,
OL,20,Fcutting off access to homes and
OL,21,Fbusinesses.
