OL,3,CCouncil looking for two lorries after
OL,4,C30 tonnes of rubbish dumped
OL,6,FContractors using a mechanical digger
OL,7,Fcleared the road, restoring access
OL,8,Falong the two-lane route on Tuesday
OL,9,Fmorning.
OL,11,FOwing to the scale of the flytipping,
OL,12,Fpolice and the district council have
OL,13,Fsaid they believe the waste has come
OL,14,Ffrom multiple businesses that paid to
OL,15,Fhave it disposed of.
