OL,3,CCouncil looking for two lorries after
OL,4,C30 tonnes of rubbish dumped
OL,6,FDrivers in the Wood End Lane area are
OL,7,Fnow being asked to contact
OL,8,Fenvironmental health officers if they
OL,9,Fhave dashcam footage to identify two
OL,10,FHGV tipper trucks that reversed into
OL,11,FWatery Lane before dumping the waste.
OL,13,FJack Twomey, Environmental Protection
OL,14,Fand Housing Manager at Lichfield
OL,15,FDistrict Council, said: "I've been
OL,16,Fdoing this job 25 years and I've never
OL,17,Fseen this before.
