OL,6,F"We've found quite a few bits of
OL,7,Fevidence they're all leading in one
OL,8,Fdirection so that's giving us quite a
OL,9,Fpositive start.
OL,11,F"So we hope to follow up on those and
OL,12,Fget somewhere with the case."
OL,14,FIn a statement he added:
OL,16,F"We have got some CCTV footage that
OL,17,Fsuggests there were two vehicles
OL,18,Finvolved.
