OL,6,F"It may be that there were more but
OL,7,Fthus far that's what it seems to be
OL,8,Fpointing towards."
OL,10,FMr Twomey estimated it may have taken
OL,11,Fbetween 30 seconds and a minute to off-
OL,12,Fload the waste on to the "reasonably
OL,13,Fwell-used" road.
OL,15,FHe said the council would also seek to
OL,16,Fseize any vehicles proven to be
OL,17,Finvolved.
